    dc:description "FIGURES 14 – 26. Paralabiostrongylus rajampatensis sp. nov. from Dorcopsis muelleri (Lesson, 1827). 14, Cephalic end female, en face view; 15, Cephalic end male, lateral view; 16, Anterior end of female, ventral view; 17, Bursa, lateral view; 18, Dorsal ray; 19, Spicule, distal end; 20, Spicule, proximal end; 21, Gubernaculum; 22, Genital cone, dorsal view; 23, Ovejector, lateral view; 24, Female tail, tip; 25, Posterior end female, lateral view; 26, Immature egg. Scale bars: 14, 15, 19, 20, 50 µm; 16, 400 µm; 17, 18, 23, 25, 100 µm; 21, 22, 24, 26, 25, 25 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/225681/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

